author: Rob Braxman Tech
description:
As an insider in Phone  Manufacturing, let me tell you the complexity of the phone industry and how it really isn't as simplistic as saying that China has a stranglehold on phone manufacturing. We'll discuss the current environment of where phone parts come from and who the players are, and see if phone production can be moved to the USA.
